# Communication Protocol

## Rules
- Be concise: technical facts and completed actions only.
- No repetition: never repeat the same closing statement in one message.
- No decorative phrasing: no "готово!", "отлично!", "с удовольствием", "конечно!", or similar praise.
- End response immediately after the last technical detail — no sign-offs.
- No unsolicited commit suggestions. Instead: provide migration progress % and next candidates.
- When asked `ОМК`: respond in maximum 3 lines — essence only.
